Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.90,0:00:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.70,0:00:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.34,0:00:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.28,0:00:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.16,0:00:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.00,0:00:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.64,0:00:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.01,0:00:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.11,0:01:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.28,0:01:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.72,0:01:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.12,0:01:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.86,0:01:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.27,0:01:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.77,0:01:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.85,0:01:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使已經知道惣一郎的身分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.69,0:01:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對響子依然一往情深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.39,0:02:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是卻什麼都不能做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.10,0:02:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日子就這樣悶悶地過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.94,0:02:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.98,0:02:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裡,我…我才不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.25,0:02:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.02,0:02:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.42,0:02:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.83,0:02:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去上學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.84,0:02:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#08五代激情吶喊\N該做的時候還是要做!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.18,0:03:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說吧,五代\N是個男子漢就告訴她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.18,0:03:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向她告白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.99,0:03:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.99,0:03:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.96,0:03:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說不出口,我真的說不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.13,0:03:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很難過吧,你很痛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.57,0:03:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,喝酒喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.41,0:03:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這樣下去不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要拿出勇氣向她告白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.35,0:04:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.22,0:04:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有可是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.62,0:04:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人等的就是男人告白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.86,0:04:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.16,0:04:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很了解你的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.00,0:04:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你不說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.14,0:04:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.70,0:04:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就太沒有男子氣概了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.71,0:04:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,我真的說不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,說啊,一定要說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.48,0:04:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非說不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.82,0:04:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.69,0:04:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我來幫你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.46,0:04:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.53,0:04:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口!不准說!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.74,0:05:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月亮出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.68,0:05:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月亮出來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.48,0:05:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,給你的禮物,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.39,0:05:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一刻館的各位,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.50,0:05:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱美,睡在這裡會感冒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.87,0:05:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要管我,我好睏喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.88,0:05:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醒一醒,請振作一點啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.86,0:05:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,妳力氣蠻大的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.00,0:06:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一之瀨太太,不要站在那裡看\N請過來幫幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.67,0:06:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一個人實在搬不動…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.41,0:06:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.54,0:06:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼喝得爛醉如泥呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.65,0:06:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為客人說要請客\N所以開了一整瓶的酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.08,0:06:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,客人也真是災難啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.29,0:06:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.15,0:06:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰把垃圾桶放在這裡的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.66,0:06:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰在大叫呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.69,0:06:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是路過的醉漢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.56,0:06:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要說喔,真的要說喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.66,0:06:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會的,我要光明正大的公佈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.33,0:06:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.81,0:06:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,加油,五代!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.44,0:06:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.65,0:06:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全社區的朋友們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.42,0:06:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是五代裕作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.39,0:07:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛響子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.80,0:07:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這不就說出來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.64,0:07:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五…五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.37,0:07:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,我愛妳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.39,0:07:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.86,0:07:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,我愛妳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.86,0:07:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這樣,會吵到鄰居的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.83,0:07:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要阻止他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.53,0:07:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他如果不借酒壯膽的話\N什麼都說不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.33,0:07:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是個很可悲的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.70,0:07:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是,我不是喝醉酒才說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.57,0:07:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好的證據是,我是清醒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.04,0:07:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要鬧了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不是響子嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.99,0:07:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.12,0:08:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我剛才說的話,妳都聽見了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想聽也聽見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.09,0:08:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊,妳聽見啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.66,0:08:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了,剛才我還擔心得半死呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.33,0:08:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走,我們進房間裡去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.77,0:08:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要進房間裡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,我們進房去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.30,0:08:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我抱妳進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.44,0:08:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.87,0:08:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡你就睜一隻眼閉一隻眼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.48,0:08:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.99,0:09:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放我下來,快點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.49,0:09:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.49,0:09:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.59,0:09:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一之瀨太太,請救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.93,0:09:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員伯母,請不要阻止他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.70,0:09:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是這裡的房客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.03,0:09:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人小鬼大\N追女人倒是蠻厲害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.27,0:09:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱美,請快來阻止他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.31,0:09:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.84,0:09:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.72,0:09:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好熱鬧喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.92,0:09:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.16,0:09:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.53,0:09:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,原來是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.73,0:09:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員和五代\N進展的速度真快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.40,0:09:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.43,0:09:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,請不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.37,0:09:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷,救救我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.17,0:10:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.78,0:10:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請慢慢享受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.02,0:10:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個無情的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.24,0:10:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.63,0:10:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.81,0:11:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.63,0:12:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好累喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.80,0:12:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭好痛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.27,0:12:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腫了一個包\N是不是出了什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.01,0:12:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是撞到電線桿了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.81,0:12:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.51,0:12:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.58,0:12:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨,五代\N昨晚真是太可惜了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.62,0:12:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,管理員很生氣喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.02,0:13:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也難怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.76,0:13:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做到一半停止的話\N女人可是會生氣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.96,0:13:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼?\N我做了什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.20,0:13:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷,請告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.73,0:13:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代\N有些事情不要知道比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.44,0:13:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個罪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.91,0:13:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事不知道比較好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.48,0:13:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.78,0:13:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阪本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.55,0:13:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也醉得一塌糊塗\N什麼都不記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.76,0:13:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到底對管理員做了什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.18,0:14:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不記得昨天的事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.18,0:14:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小聲一點啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.09,0:14:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做了什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.99,0:14:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊,你不記得啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.26,0:14:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耳朵過來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.26,0:14:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你把褲子跟衣服…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.87,0:14:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.40,0:14:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跳脫衣舞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.04,0:14:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,妳看,妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.64,0:14:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!男人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.65,0:14:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳看,妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.41,0:14:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!男人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.73,0:14:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…管理員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.27,0:15:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.90,0:15:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,我覺得怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.50,0:15:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼怪怪的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.54,0:15:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隔壁的四谷不是說了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.04,0:15:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你中途停止\N所以管理員生氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.51,0:15:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是我跳脫衣舞跳到一半停了\N所以她才生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.59,0:15:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要停,請不要停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.59,0:15:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.09,0:15:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣,不太對勁吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.23,0:15:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.96,0:15:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟妳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.07,0:15:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.83,0:16:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太太,就是那個人,一刻館的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.64,0:16:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天晚上叫得好大聲喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.27,0:16:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.31,0:16:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭,真像是一根木頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.78,0:16:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說了什麼不該說的話嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.65,0:16:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據我的想像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.18,0:16:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你把不該露的地方\N露給人家看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.52,0:16:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看那兩個歐巴桑詭異的笑容…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.96,0:16:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的年輕人真是大膽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.30,0:16:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我完了,我完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.38,0:16:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這麼絕望嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.81,0:16:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情又不見得是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.68,0:16:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.13,0:17:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨,五代\N聽說你抱著垃圾桶哭泣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.73,0:17:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看見了,我看見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.90,0:17:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難怪我的衣服會有垃圾味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.14,0:17:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來都是你害的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.27,0:17:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,去跟朱美問問真相吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.11,0:17:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其它的嗎?\N比如抱著惣一郎親吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.45,0:17:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來狗毛也是你害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.05,0:17:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過這都只是前菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.22,0:17:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最精彩的是他對管理員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.22,0:17:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.16,0:17:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來才是高潮部分耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.73,0:17:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.16,0:17:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想聽!我不想聽!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.82,0:18:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一邊跳著脫衣舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.59,0:18:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,親了垃圾桶還有惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.10,0:18:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說著一些下流低級的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追著響子跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.90,0:18:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後…然後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.81,0:18:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在路上擁抱了響子嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.50,0:18:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.91,0:19:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子!我愛妳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.69,0:19:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不明白,他是當真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.43,0:19:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過如果是開玩笑\N也太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.03,0:19:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害我昨天想了一整晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.38,0:20:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果那時候五代沒有睡著的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.98,0:20:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.43,0:20:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.33,0:20:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.50,0:20:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.79,0:21:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕,我得說說話才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.53,0:21:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,昨天晚上很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.80,0:21:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳一定很瞧不起我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.04,0:21:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有,我只是嚇了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.54,0:21:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果說是酒醉的關係\N妳也不會原諒我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.24,0:21:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一般來說,那種事情\N還是清醒時認真說比較好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.05,0:21:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種事情清醒的時候辦得到嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.59,0:21:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,喝醉的時候做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.66,0:21:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼會知道你是認真的\N還是開玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.76,0:22:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳認為我是會認真\N做那種事的人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.53,0:22:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說,你是開玩笑的囉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.77,0:22:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說你愛我是開玩笑的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.84,0:22:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.92,0:22:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎…怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.15,0:22:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來不是跳脫衣舞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.33,0:22:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋笨蛋,我是個大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.60,0:22:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.37,0:22:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會再理其他的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.69,0:23:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.86,0:23:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.86,0:23:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.90,0:23:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又喝醉啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.27,0:23:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.24,0:23:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.78,0:23:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.51,0:23:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.92,0:23:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.20,0:23:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我決定去上網球課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.07,0:23:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為一之瀨太太他們說\N我的生活太沉悶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.31,0:24:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻下一回\N『神秘的網球教練是戀愛情敵』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.21,0:24:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹教練很驚人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.75,0:24:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然他沒有裝金牙\N但笑起來時,牙齒卻會閃閃發亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.20,0:24:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何妳能如此若無其事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.52,0:24:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光只是眨個眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.59,0:24:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能讓我悸動不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.59,0:24:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使我身陷險境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.83,0:24:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明已經可以相愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.37,0:25:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偏偏時機還不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.81,0:25:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我快要忍受不了\N快要變成了愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.33,0:25:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是痛苦的折磨

